<refnamediv id='pl-name'>
  <refname>pl</refname>
  <refpurpose>PL_TDF compiler producing TDF</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv id='pl-synopsis'>
  <cmdsynopsis>
    <command>pl</command>
    <arg choice='opt'>-I <replaceable>path</replaceable></arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>-g</arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>-p</arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>-V</arg>
    <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>infile.pl</replaceable></arg>
    <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>outfile.j</replaceable></arg>
  </cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>


<refsect1 id='pl-description'>
  <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
  <para>The action of <command>pl</command> is to compile a PL_TDF text in
    <emphasis>infile.pl</emphasis> to a TDF capsule in
    <emphasis>outfile.j</emphasis>. (See <emphasis>PL_TDF Definition</emphasis>).
    The resulting .j file is suitable for linking and translation by
    &man.tendra.tcc;</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1 id='pl-options'>
  <title>OPTIONS</title>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-I</option> <replaceable>path</replaceable></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Gives the search path for any #include files in the PL_TDF
          text.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-V</option></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>This option causes <command>pl</command> to print its version
          number and the version of the TDF specification it supports.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-g</option></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Add debug information such as line number and source filename 
          in the output TDF capsule.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-h</option>, <option>--help</option></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Prints a summary of all options.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-p</option></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>This option produces a "pretty print" of the TDF capsule on the
          standard output.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</refsect1>

<refsect1 id='pl-seealso'>
<title>SEE ALSO</title>
